high_descs: Turn left and head left to the sink.
Pick up the egg in the right side of the sink.
Turn around and walk left around the kitchen island all the way to the microwave in the corner.
Place the egg in the microwave to the left of the apple.
Turn left and walk along the counter to the fridge.
Take the egg out of the fridge.
Turn right and walk back to the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave to the right of the apple.
